## Step 5 – Configure End Devices

For each PC/Server in Packet Tracer:
1. Click the device → go to **Desktop** tab → **IP Configuration**
2. Set the IP, subnet mask, and default gateway as shown in the table below:

| Device     | IP Address     | Subnet Mask     | Default Gateway |
|------------|----------------|-----------------|-----------------|
| Admin-PC   | 10.10.10.10    | 255.255.255.0   | 10.10.10.1      |
| User-PC-1  | 10.10.20.10    | 255.255.255.0   | 10.10.20.1      |
| User-PC-2  | 10.10.20.11    | 255.255.255.0   | 10.10.20.1      |
| Web-Server | 10.10.30.10    | 255.255.255.0   | 10.10.30.1      |
| DNS-Server | 10.10.30.11    | 255.255.255.0   | 10.10.30.1      |

