## ✅ Verification Commands

Run these to confirm everything is working:

```bash
# On Core Switch — check VLANs exist
show vlan brief

# Check trunk ports are up
show interfaces trunk

# Check routing table
show ip route

# Check ACLs are applied
show ip access-lists
show ip interface vlan 20

# On any PC — test basic connectivity
ping 10.10.10.1       ! Should succeed (same VLAN gateway)
ping 10.10.30.10      ! Users: only HTTP should work (ACL)
ping 10.10.10.10      ! Users: should FAIL (blocked by ACL)
```
